videos.description: David Nichols tosses it up to Devin Vassell on the baseline for an alley-oop jam.
videos.headline: Vassell gets up to throw down alley-oop

videos.description: Terance Mann drives to the basket and lobs it up to Christ Koumadje for a Florida State jam.
videos.headline: 7-4 Koumadje slams lob

videos.description: M.J. Walker swats a Georgia Tech layup then Mfiondu Kabengele dunks it on the other end to extend Florida State's lead.
videos.headline: Walker's chase-down block leads to wide-open dunk
